 presents detailed proofs throughout the book. Most undergraduate books on mathematical logic are written for a reader who is well-versed in logical notation and mathematical proof. This textbook is written to attract a wider audience, including students who are not yet experts in the art of mathematical proof.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 4aDeduktives Denken. 4aLogik erster Ordnung. 4aLogik zweiter Ordnung. 4aMathematische Logik. 7aPHILOSOPHY / Logic.2bisacsh  aMathematical logic, logic of the first order, logic of the second order, deductive reasoning.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2023 Part 1z978311117578208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishz978311131929208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023z9783111318912oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Mathematics 2023 Englishz978311131920908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Mathematics 2023z9783111318608oZDB-23-DMA0 cEPUBz97831107821960 cprintz978311078201140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311078207340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110782073423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110782073/original  a978-3-11-117578-2  DG Plus DeG Package 2023 Part 1b2023  a978-3-11-131920-9  EBOOK PACKAGE Mathematics 2023 Englishb2023  a978-3-11-131929-2  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishb2023  aEBA_CL_MTPY  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_MTPY  aEBA_ECL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_ESTMALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2023  aZDB-23-DMAb2023